{"word":"Security","slug":"security","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Security</b> For debt<br/> <a href='S:Debt'>Debt</a>; <a href='S:Surety'>Surety</a><br/> False security<br/> - Promises peace and long life<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=18&chapter=29&verse=18'>Job 29:18</a> <br/> - Is ignorant of God and truth<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=10&verse=4'>Psa 10:4</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=50&verse=21'>Psa 50:21</a> <br/> - Trusts in lies<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=28&verse=15'>Isa 28:15</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=66&chapter=3&verse=17'>Rev 3:17</a> <br/> - Is inconsiderate and forgetful<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=47&verse=7'>Isa 47:7</a> <br/> - Relies on earthly treasures<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=49&verse=4'>Jer 49:4</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=49&verse=16'>Jer 49:16</a> <br/> - Is deceived by pride<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=31&chapter=1&verse=3'>Oba 1:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=66&chapter=18&verse=7'>Rev 18:7</a> <br/> - Puts off the evil day<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=30&chapter=6&verse=3'>Amo 6:3</a> <br/> - Leads to increased guilt<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=21&chapter=8&verse=11'>Ecc 8:11</a> <br/> - Its refuge shall be scattered<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=28&verse=17'>Isa 28:17</a> <br/> - Ruin shall overtake it<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=47&verse=9'>Isa 47:9</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=30&chapter=9&verse=10'>Amo 9:10</a> <br/> - God is against it<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=21&verse=13'>Jer 21:13</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=39&verse=6'>Eze 39:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=30&chapter=6&verse=1'>Amo 6:1</a><br/><a href='S:Confidence, False'>Confidence, False</a>; <a href='S:Self-Deception'>Self-deception</a>; <a href='S:Self-Delusion'>Self-delusion</a> "}]}